*   ## **_WWE CHAMPIONSHIP: CODY RHODES DEF. KEVIN OWENS_**
    

The story of this match is that Kevin Owens has lost his edge. He refused to take advantage of Cody Rhodes knee injury and it eventually cost him.

What an excellent match. What a great way to open WWE Bash in Berlin 👏🏾👏🏾👏🏾👏🏾

