*   ## **_WWE WOMEN'S TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: JADE CARGILL AND BIANCA BELAIR DEF. UNHOLY UNION(c)_**
    

New Champions after a pretty awkward match. The crowd never died tho!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/232ad095-d992-4103-99de-5d340d126cdb/20240831_110422.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/de966438-5e8a-4f56-a797-1dcffa3941d0/20240831_112331.jpg)

*   ## **_STRAP MATCH: CM PUNK DEF. DREW MCINTYRE_**
    

All four corners of the ring must be touched in succession.

Drew takes the advantage before Punk can finish his entrance and doesn't let up. He eventually straps Punk himself and then Punk actually hits a GTS very early on.

He could've won the match but he decided to keep attacking Drew instead.

They brawl to the outside where Punk gets busted open. Very good back and forth action. Punk is able to hit McIntyre with a GTS before Drew can hit the fourth corner.

Punk begins hitting the corners and everytime Drew gets up to stop him, he's hit with another GTS. Punk takes back his bracelet after the 3rd GTS. He taps the fourth corner and wins his first WWE match in 10 years.

