![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c17ab9cf-bd57-4200-bb7d-24fcedd6dd47/20240831_120858.jpg)

*   ## **_TERROR TWINS DEF. DOM AND LIV MORGAN_**
    

Dom and Liv try every single one of their tricks including calling down the rest of Judgement Day. But the wrath of the Terror Twins was just too much. CLEAN VICTORY OVER THE JUDGEMENT DAY

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0bb1b300-5d33-4406-aed2-42ef0761309c/Screenshot_20240831_124756.jpg)

*   ## **_WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP: GUNTHER VS RANDY ORTON_**
    

INCREDIBLE atmosphere for this match.

Orton takes out GUNTHER’s arm early on, which eliminated a lot of GUNTHER's offense for most of the match. Randy had control until Gunther finally reversed an RKO into a German suplex. Gunther takes control for only a bit before Orton finally hits an RKO

Orton actually puts GUNTHER through a table with a back drop off of some steel steps at one point. Gunther eventually puts Randy Orton to sleep to retain.

He extends his hand to Randy Orton out of respect